Levelling Formula

5 * (lvl ^ 2) + (50 * lvl) + 100 - xp

Paramters

    lvl is the currentl level of the user
    xp is the current xp of the user


Levelling Rewards
-----------------

Top 10 messengers of the week get x role with colour.
Top 10 messengers of the month get custom role with colour (expires at the end of the month)

5, 10 etc role levels 


Levelling Changes
-----------------

Update schema to keep the level in the user's profile too
Create handlers for level checks, role settings/auto creation
Add a xp blacklist for users and channels


Possible Features
-----------------

Creating webhooks and setting for repo in github
Storage of invites and who joined from them